OL,3,CTop City bosses paid a record #4.19m
OL,4,Con average last year
OL,6,FThe bosses of Britain's top firms
OL,7,Freceived the biggest average pay
OL,8,Fpacket on record last year, according
OL,9,Fto research.
OL,11,FMedian pay for a FTSE 100 chief
OL,12,Fexecutive was #4.19 million in 2023,
OL,13,Fup from #4.1 million in 2022, a 2.2%
OL,14,Fincrease, said the High Pay Centre.
OL,16,FThis is the highest ever figure,
OL,17,Falthough the growth in CEO pay was
OL,18,Fslower than in the past two years,
OL,19,Fwhen there was post-pandemic bounce.
