OL,6,FThe best paid boss on the FTSE 100 was
OL,7,FAstraZeneca's Pascal Soriot, who made
OL,8,F#16.85 million.
OL,10,FErik Engstrom, boss of analytics giant
OL,11,FRELX, was next with #13.64 million,
OL,12,Ffollowed by Rolls-Royce CEO Tufan
OL,13,FErginbilgic with #13.61 million.
OL,15,FHigh pay at Britain's biggest firms
OL,16,Fhas come under the spotlight in recent
OL,17,Ftimes, following a cost-of-living
OL,18,Fcrisis sparked by a period of sky-high
OL,19,Fmortgage rates, inflation and energy
OL,20,Fbills between 2021 and 2023.
