OL,6,FThe High Pay Centre's research shows
OL,7,Fthat the median FTSE 100 CEO is now
OL,8,Fpaid 120 times the median UK full-time
OL,9,Fworker, down from 124 times in 2022,
OL,10,Fbut still higher than 108 times in
OL,11,F2021.
OL,13,FThe High Pay Centre report argued that
OL,14,Fexcessive spending on top earners by
OL,15,Fleading firms makes it harder to fund
OL,16,Fpay increases for the wider UK
OL,17,Fworkforce.
