OL,6,FThe think tank called for reforms to
OL,7,Frules around corporate pay-setting
OL,8,Fprocess, including a requirement for
OL,9,Fcompanies to include a minimum of two
OL,10,Felected workforce representatives on
OL,11,Fthe committees that set pay.
OL,13,FNonetheless, the rises come after
OL,14,Fpleas for bigger and better pay
OL,15,Fpackages for City bosses.
OL,17,FDame Julia Hoggett, CEO of the London
OL,18,FStock Exchange, said earlier this year
OL,19,Fthat chiefs are being paid
OL,20,F"significantly below global
OL,21,Fbenchmarks".
