OL,6,F"The huge pay gap between executives
OL,7,Fand the wider UK workforce is a result
OL,8,Fof factors like the decline of trade
OL,9,Funion membership, low levels of worker
OL,10,Fparticipation in business decision-
OL,11,Fmaking and a business culture that
OL,12,Fputs the interests of investors before
OL,13,Fworkers, customers, suppliers and
OL,14,Fother stakeholders.
